---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Yilong Scrubs - 20 years of medical apparel manufacturing expertise. 100% focused on scrubs.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Our Story</div>
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-extrabold mb-12">20 Years of Craftsmanship</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-xl prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-16">
        <p>Born in the heart of professional garment manufacturing, Yilong Scrubs has spent 20 years perfecting the art of the medical uniform. Our journey began with a simple mission: to provide healthcare heroes with the armor they deserve—comfortable, functional, and durable.</p>
        
        <p>Unlike general apparel factories, we are **100% focused on medical scrubs**. This specialization allows us to deeply understand fabric dynamics and ergonomic design needs specific to medical work environments.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 py-16 border-y border-slate-100 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-primary mb-2">20</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Years Experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-secondary mb-2">100%</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Scrubs Focused</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-orange-600 mb-2">Global</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Market Reach</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-12 rounded-3xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-6 italic">Global Reach</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Serving healthcare brands in North America, Europe, and Australia with high-performance medical apparel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-12 rounded-3xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-6 italic">Factory Direct</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">No middlemen. You get direct access to our 20 years of manufacturing know-how and competitive pricing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
